==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin [[bestia]] : animal, beast

===Noun===
'''beast'''
#any [[animal]] other than a [[human]]; usually only applied to [[vertebrate]]s, sometimes excluding [[bird]]s.
#a person who [[behave]]s in a violent, antisocial or uncivilised manner

